BT /F1 12 Tf 72 678 Td(Sakum is an agentic AI runtime written entirely in x86-64 assembly) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 664 Td(No libc, no runtime, no dependencies -- raw BSD syscalls only) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 650 Td(Inspired by human immune system: danger theory + self-healing) Tj ET
