BT /F1 12 Tf 72 412 Td(1. DETECT: Health checks, heartbeat timeouts, invariant violations) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 398 Td(2. DIAGNOSE: Root cause isolation via dependency graph) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 384 Td(3. HEAL: Restart component, rollback state, re-route traffic) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 370 Td(4. VERIFY: Post-heal health check, metric regression test) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 72 356 Td() Tj ET
